ygData.messageBody:
I was running Hally to Karnors this morning from FV and at one point, I was
SURROUNDED by those spiders. I was sooooo queezed out. OMG. I mean I was
seriously almost shaking. Do they have counseling for this kind of stuff? I
think I'm scarred for life.

Ok, I promise I'll stop obsessing about the spiders now...

-----Original Message-----
From: Perhaps a Princess... [mailto:sarah@...]
Sent: Wednesday, May 17, 2000 11:09 AM
To: eqbards@egroups.com
Subject: RE: [eqbards] kunark level 21

Lake of Ill Omen.

I went to Kunark at level 19 and have worked my way up to
Level 26, mostly
in the Lake, but also in Warsliks Wood, fighting Forest
Giants.
I am ready now to go to Frontier Mountains.

The hardest part of Kunark is getting through Firiona Vie
without
being slaughtered by the spiders.

If you can, get someone to invis you. SOme see thorugh
invisibile,
but most don't.
